properties.areaDesc: Port Washington to North Point Light WI; Sheboygan to Port Washington WI; Wind Point WI to Winthrop Harbor IL; North Point Light to Wind Point WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 16 at 8:38PM CST until February 18 at 12:00PM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
GUSTY WINDS WILL DEVELOP MONDAY MORNING AND CONTINUE INTO
TUESDAY...

* WHAT...Light and variable winds will becoming east to southeast
and increase to 15 to 20 knots, with gusts to 25 knots Monday
morning. Waves will build to 4 to 7 feet. The gusty winds will
become northwest on Tuesday.

* WHERE...Near shore waters from Sheboygan to Winthrop Harbor IL.

* WHEN...From 9 AM Monday to noon CST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM MONDAY TO NOON CST TUESDAY
